{"tid":1854754,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動］抗爭 抗疫 雙線進行！ 做野啦 屌！","createTime":"2020-01-31T16:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T18:36:15.000Z","uid":137699,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6107c44c0d77a270d72f80891d033c637955fc4e","tid":1854754,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"唔做標題黨 <br />\n再講多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地究竟做緊乜撚？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n成個連登熱門都係口罩同肺炎？<br />\n而加連登變左新聞台？ <br />\n唔講以為呢場運動已經完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗鄉黑又出黎做野 冇人講<br />\n今晚旺角又大圍捕 冇人講<br />\n聯罩 唔夠人簽<br />\nTwitter 任務唔夠人做<br />\n連儂牆文宣 冇人做</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該大家 <br />\n睇完呢個post 做番正經野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[size=5]<strong>抗爭 同 抗疫 要同時進行<br />\n唔好當手足係口罩 <br />\n唔係用完即棄架！！</strong></span></span><br />\n係屋企唔代表冇野可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊做Twitter 任務！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=a672f26c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊簽聯罩！！！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【香港人係咪放棄咗？】白宮聯署：香港真普選計劃，欠50,429，2月1日截止！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854447</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊 十點鳩叫 ！！！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對症下藥 封關救港<br />\n支持醫護 全民罷工<br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔出街都可以做到 <br />\n如果你地咁都做唔到 <br />\n唔好叫自己香港人 你唔配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做正經野啦 屌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7550d17801810543160d401b53aa20d39a2395b1","tid":1854754,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"[行動］運動靜咗？驚咗肺炎？仲有樣嘢可以做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842695</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a0d5f7088b6f0704001fab4b8e1272ab03162e6","tid":1854754,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:09:22.000Z","msg":"［內有口罩link ］運動已完 齊心搶口罩！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854704</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"958e61ad2c2fa7cb127560537cf5fd6c4617e532","tid":1854754,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"緊急⚠️⚠️冇人知今日醫護有野搞！！<br />\n幫我入去十連！！<br />\n<br />\n「全城集氣撐醫護！！」今日三個行程終極懶人包！我要所有人出嚟集氣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"80095a4272f34b2619a4b03e38cf9c5a1be6b588","tid":1854754,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:10:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/f